gonna take back before Emma...

742
01:05:17,127 --> 01:05:18,879
...I think I can get it working.

743
01:05:21,047 --> 01:05:22,366
What?

744
01:05:23,327 --> 01:05:26,922
- We're not going anywhere.
- What, are you planning...

745
01:05:27,087 --> 01:05:30,079
