and waiting for more to come?

746
01:05:30,247 --> 01:05:32,317
[♪♪♪]

747
01:05:32,487 --> 01:05:34,318
What makes you think
more are coming?

748
01:05:34,487 --> 01:05:36,159
The fuck are you saying?

749
01:05:36,327 --> 01:05:37,760
They're coming.

750
01:05:37,927 --> 01:05:41,556
If it's not today, it'll be tomorrow
or next week, but they're back.

751
01:05:41,727 --> 01:05:44,878
Shit. You're worried
about her brushing her teeth...

752
01:05:45,047 --> 01:05:48,005
...instead of her living her life
cooped up in this prison.

753
01:05:48,167 --> 01:05:49,805
There is no future here, Jack.

754
01:05:49,967 --> 01:05:52,800
You lower your voice,
or you will wake her up.

755
01:05:53,647 --> 01:05:56,002
We are safe here.

756
01:05:56,967 --> 01:05:59,686
We can protect ourselves here.

757
01:06:00,047 --> 01:06:02,083
We have no idea
what's on the other side.

758
01:06:02,247 --> 01:06:04,966
That's the problem, Jack.
We don't know shit.

759
01:06:05,287 --> 01:06:08,404
You have been so hell-bent
on surviving...

760
01:06:08,567 --> 01:06:11,525
