What did you do?

777
01:07:21,287 --> 01:07:22,322
Emma's...

778
01:07:24,367 --> 01:07:26,323
Do you know what you've done?

779
01:07:26,487 --> 01:07:29,524
The infected are all gone.
They're not...

780
01:07:29,807 --> 01:07:31,638
You son of a bitch.

781
01:07:31,807 --> 01:07:34,037
Fuck off.

782
01:07:35,607 --> 01:07:37,916
It's okay. It's okay.

783
01:07:39,887 --> 01:07:41,206
Where is she?

784
01:07:42,247 --> 01:07:44,397
- What?
- Emma. Where is she?

785
01:07:49,887 --> 01:07:51,639
You fucking killed her.

786
01:07:51,807 --> 01:07:53,126
Fuck.

787
01:07:53,927 --> 01:07:55,246
Fuck you.

788
01:07:59,647 --> 01:08:01,558
[SOBBING]

789
01:08:02,487 --> 01:08:04,717
You're no longer her father.

790
01:08:06,247 --> 01:08:08,158
[♪♪♪]

791
01:08:21,887 --> 01:08:23,798
[GROWLING]

792
01:08:30,087 --> 01:08:31,998
[DISTANT HOWLING]

793
01:08:34,487 --> 01:08:35,806
Dad.

794
01:08:35,967 --> 01:08:37,241
